name: Dr. Beetle's lab
description:
Based off of the "Girl Genius" comic by Phil Foglio.
This work was not approved by, sponsored by, or affiliated with Studio Foglio LLC or Airship Entertainment.
Please visit: http://girlgeniusonline.com/

I modeled the interior of the lab based on comics starting here:
http://www.girlgeniusonline.com/comic.php?date=20021206
Very little license has been taken with the scene. Some parts of the Dihoxulator are never seen in the comic (and probably never will be) so I fleshed it out as best I could. Very rewarding to work from such a technically excellent source. Phil Foglio maintains consistency between vastly differing views, which made it much easier to model the lab. I hope you enjoy it, and take a look at the comic!

Like this model, but need something a bit different? I take commissions! http://peripheralarbor.com/commission/
